      "retweeted_tweet_id": null,
      "text": "UNVETTED AFGHAN PEDOPHILE ARRESTED.\n\nBasir Ahmad Safi, an Afghan national, was arrested by DHS on March 11. Safi has a disgusting criminal history, including indecent exposure to a minor, soliciting a child by computer, child abuse, and lascivious exhibition.\n\nSafi was allowed into our homeland in 2021 as a part of President Biden’s \"Operation Allies Welcome” and was arrested only two years later for his sex offenses.\n\nHe should have NEVER been allowed into America and given the opportunity to prey on innocent children. DHS will continue to identify and remove the public safety threats, like Safi, within our nation.",
      "text_resolved": "UNVETTED AFGHAN PEDOPHILE ARRESTED.\n\nBasir Ahmad Safi, an Afghan national, was arrested by DHS on March 11. Safi has a disgusting criminal history, including indecent exposure to a minor, soliciting a child by computer, child abuse, and lascivious exhibition.\n\nSafi was allowed into our homeland in 2021 as a part of President Biden’s \"Operation Allies Welcome” and was arrested only two years later for his sex offenses.\n\nHe should have NEVER been allowed into America and given the opportunity to prey on innocent children. DHS will continue to identify and remove the public safety threats, like Safi, within our nation.",
      "lang": "en",
