      "text": "CANINE CRUSADER. \n\nOne of our brave and beautiful @CBP K9’s uncovered 32 POUNDS of COCAINE hidden within a floor compartment of a vehicle during a checkpoint inspection in the Tucson Sector.\n\nOur K9 warriors play a vital role in our mission of stopping all illegal drugs from crossing the border and harming the American people. \n\nSecuring the border secures America, and we will always fight to eliminate the scourge of drugs.",
      "text_resolved": "CANINE CRUSADER. \n\nOne of our brave and beautiful @CBP K9’s uncovered 32 POUNDS of COCAINE hidden within a floor compartment of a vehicle during a checkpoint inspection in the Tucson Sector.\n\nOur K9 warriors play a vital role in our mission of stopping all illegal drugs from crossing the border and harming the American people. \n\nSecuring the border secures America, and we will always fight to eliminate the scourge of drugs.",
